# Razdolye, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Razdolye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tarumovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 9 streets.
Geography
Razdolye is located 15&nbsp;km north of Tarumovka (the district's administrative centre) by road. Talovka is the nearest rural locality.
